title: Hong Kong Terms of Trade
description: Terms of Trade in Hong Kong decreased to 98.90 points in September from 100.20 points in August of 2022. Terms of Trade in Hong Kong averaged 102.76 points from 1982 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 108.50 points in July of 1985 and a record low of 98.80 points in September of 2021. In Hong Kong, Terms of Trade (ToT) correspond to the ratio of Price of exportable goods to the Price of importable goods. This page provides - Hong Kong Terms of Trade - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Census and Statistics Department, Hong Kong
